lead_paragraph: Michael Saunders homered twice and drove in five runs, leading the Toronto Blue Jays to a 9-6 victory over the Philadelphia Phillies on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Saunders Homers Twice as Blue Jays Beat Phillies 9-6
